casebody.data:
RB ALDEN CORP., Appellee
v.
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Appellant RB Alden Corp., Cross-Appellant
v.
Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, Cross-Appellee No. 60 MAP 2017
No. 66 MAP 2017 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Decided: September 21, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM

AND NOW, this 21 st day of September, 2018, the order of the Commonwealth Court is VACATED , and this matter is REMANDED to the Commonwealth Court for reconsideration in light of this Court's decision in Nextel v. Commonwealth , 642 Pa. 729 , 171 A.3d 682 (2017). Further, the Commonwealth's "Application to Strike, In Part, RB Alden Corp.'s Reply Brief" is DENIED as moot.
